The Sub Court, Manjeri, in O.P. (Arbitration) Ext.P6 in O.P.(C)No. No.1/2023 finding that the 2650/2023 Award is not stayed as per Sec.36 (3) of the Act;
that no application under Sec.36 (3) is made by the petitioner authority and the respondent company cannot be directed to keep alive the bank guarantee against the findings rendered in the Arbitral O.P.(C).Nos. 2612 & 2650 of 2023 Sl. Date Event Remarks No. Award.
Note: The second Original Petition, O.P.(C) No. 2650 of 2023, is preferred by the petitioner authority challenging the above order of the Sub Court, Manjeri.
